Building Windows Installer for TORCS
------------------------------------
Required tools from nsis.sourceforge.net (GPL):
- NSIS 2.04
- HM NIS EDIT 2.0.2

- Build a TORCS release and copy the runtime directory into this (here).
- Rename the runtime to base.
- Open torcs.nsi with HM NIS EDIT 2.0.2 and compile the installer.


